room_title: Escape room "Escape The Undead" by Operation Outbreak in El Paso
review: WHAT A GREAT TIME! I thought this room was going to be similar to a haunted house and was hesitant to try it out at first, but boy was I wrong! Had an amazing time with the group I was paired with. Will be coming back for more!

room_title: Escape room "Escape The Undead" by Operation Outbreak in El Paso
review: Game really didn’t have many clues to solve and the entire game was played in the dark. Bring your own flashlights or make sure your phones are fully charged as the flashlight you find in the first room didn’t work. The room wasn’t bad but it wasn’t good either, somewhere in the middle
